om/l/?uddg=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Flangchain4j%2Flangchain4j%2Fblob%2Fmain%2Fdocs%2Fdocs%2Ftutorials%2Ftools.md&rut=f5a118cb0b070b463ee24c9683331a6a346925619e7cc9e0e1ef73ce4e2ec86e\nSnippet: LangChain4j is an idiomatic, open-source Java library for building LLM-powered applications on the JVM. It offers a unified API over popular LLM providers and vector stores, and makes implementing tool calling (including MCP support), agents and RAG easy.\n\n"
